 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/c5b3dbbec01976294d097cbc0de54620-kix.pm9ou9iyxjbb-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/c5b3dbbec01976294d097cbc0de54620-kix.pm9ou9iyxjbb-300x158.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/c5b3dbbec01976294d097cbc0de54620-kix.pm9ou9iyxjbb-768x404.webp 768w" width="1000" height="526" /></a></p><p>在游戏过程中，您将通过每次训练课程增加您的人数，并在训练期间进行对话。内容虽然简单，但也有保存、积压等实用功能，用起来相当舒服。画面很华丽，除了制作人之外还有其他声音。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/c5b3dbbec01976294d097cbc0de54620-kix.x1nm68ie17wo-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/c5b3dbbec01976294d097cbc0de54620-kix.x1nm68ie17wo-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/c5b3dbbec01976294d097cbc0de54620-kix.x1nm68ie17wo-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/c5b3dbbec01976294d097cbc0de54620-kix.x1nm68ie17wo-300x158.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/c5b3dbbec01976294d097cbc0de54620-kix.x1nm68ie17wo-768x404.webp 768w" width="1000" height="526" /></a></p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/c5b3dbbec01976294d097cbc0de54620-kix.wqszwqwapcth-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/c5b3dbbec01976294d097cbc0de54620-kix.wqszwqwapcth-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/c5b3dbbec01976294d097cbc0de54620-kix.wqszwqwapcth-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/c5b3dbbec01976294d097cbc0de54620-kix.wqszwqwapcth-300x158.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/04/c5b3dbbec01976294d097cbc0de54620-kix.wqszwqwapcth-768x404.webp 768w" width="1000" height="526" /></a></p><p>最重要的是，游戏的气氛让我感到惊讶，这与我对异世界的表现的印象完全相反。没有特别严肃的故事，整个故事温馨又过瘾。训练中也出现了迷你角色，强调了整体的可爱性，这一点还是不错的。一轮很短，所以你可以轻松地玩。</p><p>这款游戏是ヰSekaijou和KAMITSUBAKI STUDIO的粉丝必看的游戏，但也推荐给知道名字但从未听过这首歌的人。如果你玩完这个游戏后听他的歌声，你可能会被拉进缝隙里！</p><p><a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2872930/project_canvas/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>点击此处查看Steam官方网站</strong></a></p><p>（参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000093.000106737.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">新闻稿</a></p><p>这篇文章<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/project-canvas-game/">我以为是愚人节玩笑，没想到是真的。一款以虚拟歌手世界为主题的偶像养成游戏已经在Steam上免费发布了。我确实玩过它。</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; 
